    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Append Current Date to Filename in Bash Shell]]></title>
    <link href="http://leetschau.github.io/blog/2013/10/15/153027/"/>
    <updated>2013-10-15T15:30:27+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://leetschau.github.io/blog/2013/10/15/153027</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>The following command ziped all files and sub-dirs in CWD into file &ldquo;ESB_3.0_2013-10-15.zip&rdquo;:</p>

<p>$ zip build/ESB_3.0_$(date +%Y-%m-%d).zip -r .</p>

<p>Note: the blank after &ldquo;date&rdquo; is mandatory.</p>
]]></content>
